refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public array Imagick::getOptions stringpattern"*"
Returns an associative array of the options set on the wand whose names match the given pattern. Options are format-specific settings that control how images are encoded or decoded, such as jpeg:sampling-factor or png:bit-depth.

&reftitle.parameters;
pattern
A shell-style glob pattern matched against option names. The default "*" matches every option.
